items.headline: Bienvenue sur Reborn Wiki
items.desc: Ce wikia francophone est consacré à tout l'univers de Kateikyoushi Hitman REBORN! (Mon prof le tueur Reborn! en français). Kateikyoushi Hitman REBORN! est un shonen manga réalisé et dessiné par la mangaka Akira Amano. Il a été prépublié dans le Weekly Shonen Jump par les éditions Shueisha depuis avril 2004. L'anime a été adapté sur les écrans japonais en 2006 par le studio Artland. En France, le manga est publié par Glénat depuis septembre 2006 et est diffusé sur la chaîne KZTV depuis décembre 2011.

items.name: Roleplay Reborn Wiki
items.title: Roleplay Reborn Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Roleplay Reborn Wiki!
items.desc:
What do you get when you force twenty-two teenagers to live on a run-down island, and make them compete in deadly challenges to win a hundred thousand bucks? Drama... and that's what Camp Drama is all about. These fame-hungry youngsters are forced to endure a summer of leaky cabins, polluted water, and crappy food prepared by a tough-as-nails ex-army general.
In this jaw-dropping roleplay, alliances are formed, friendships are put to the test, and romances blossom, up until the very last episode, where the last two standing will compete in a final challenge to win the ultimate grand prize.

items.name: Final Fantasy A Realm Reborn Wiki
items.title: Final Fantasy A Realm Reborn Wiki
items.headline: Explore Final Fantasy XIV: A Realm Reborn
items.desc: Form a party and adventure with a multitude of players from across the globe. Forge friendships, mount chocobos, and board airships as you and your companions create your own unique stories in Eorzea. Set out alone or enlist the aid of friends as you undertake epic quests, battle familiar Final Fantasy monsters, and acquire unique abilities and equipment. All the classic elements from the series that you have come to know and love are waiting! Embark on the adventure of a lifetime to help reforge the fate of Eorzea!

items.name: *Warrior Cats Reborn* Wiki
items.title: *Warrior Cats Reborn* Wiki
items.headline: ~Warrior Cats Reborn Wikia~
items.desc:
A flashing pelt crosses your vision in the night, and suddenly you see streams of cats slipping down the slope of the hill, their paws thundering on the packed earth.
ShadowClan, ThunderClan, RiverClan, WindClan, EarthClan, SkyClan, FireClan, and MoonClan racing down at your paws.
What do you do? That's right, you join.
But where do your loyalties lie? Join to find out!

items.name: Chaos Reborn Wiki
items.title: Chaos Reborn Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Chaos Reborn wikia!
items.desc:
Based on the cult classic ZX Spectrum game Chaos, first published in 1985 by Games Workshop, Chaos Reborn is part sequel, part re-imagining of that original game brought up-to-date with high quality presentation.

The magic combat system remains true to the original Chaos. It is all about summoning a host of weird and mythical creatures, moving and fighting with them, and using your wizard to attack, defend, buff, and debuff with large array of spells. It is highly tactical and fast paced. But Chaos Reborn expands considerably on this by offering multiplayer modes, a single-player RPG system, and co-op play.

items.name: Charmed Reborn Wiki
items.title: Charmed Reborn Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Charmed Reborn Wiki, the Charmed Legacy continues.
items.desc: Evil has been reborn and a new generation of Twice-blessed Halliwells were born under the elder's noses. As The Source returns to reclaim the throne of the Underworld, all demons new and old decide they have a score to settle. The Charmed Ones have new friends, enemies, powers, spells and everything they'll need to survive the demons, now can they survive high school?

items.name: Home Tutor Reborn Wiki
items.title: Home Tutor Reborn Wiki
items.desc: Tsuna, a timid junior high student, is a failure at school, sports, and social life. But everything around Tsuna has been completely changed when a baby called Reborn, who claims to be an Italian hit man from Vongola family shows up! Reborn was sent to groom Tsuna for his future life as a mafia boss of the family!
